SELECT 
  1 as eventoId,
  1 as formandoId,
  '2026-01-15 10:00:00' as dataVenda,
  100000 as valorTotal,
  'cancelada' as status,
  'Execução' as fase,
  1 as createdBy,
  1 as excluido,
  1 as excluidoPor,
  NOW() as excluidoEm,
  'Teste do sistema - validação de filtro' as motivoExclusao
LIMIT 1
